<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然說<delay8 />剛才身體狀況很差，<delay20 />
但難得你都來了，<delay8 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />卻沒聊到什麼話，真是抱歉。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />多虧<tag a="115" b="0" arg="0xcd00" />送來的<colour id="1" />藥<colour id="65535" />，<delay8 />
我現在好多了，<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />已經不用再擔心我了！<delay20 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay8 />你又來看我啦！<delay frames="30" />
我變得這麼有精神，<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay8 />嚇到你了嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實是<delay8 /><tag a="115" b="0" arg="0xcd00" /><delay8 />
帶了<colour id="1" />藥<colour id="65535" />來給我，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且這藥效<delay8 />真的是非常驚人！
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以說<delay20 /><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我已經沒事了，
你大可放心！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />上次<delay8 />謝謝你
來我家探病！<pageBreak /><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那時候<delay8 />我因為把身子搞壞了，<delay20 />
沒辦法招待你，<delay8 /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是不好意思。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />後來<delay8 /><tag a="115" b="0" arg="0xcd00" /><delay8 />
有帶了<colour id="1" />藥<colour id="65535" />來給我吃！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />多虧這樣，<delay8 />我已經恢復精神了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對了對了，<delay frames="40" /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />
上次<delay8 />謝謝你來探病！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在那之後，<delay8 /><tag a="115" b="0" arg="0xcd00" />
送來的<colour id="1" />藥<colour id="65535" />真是藥到病除，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />正如你所見，<delay20 />我已經完全康復啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實<delay8 />我得了感冒，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Hot" target="actor" targetSpec="" />直到剛剛<delay8 />都還昏昏沉沉的。<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />多虧<tag a="115" b="0" arg="0xcd00" />帶了<colour id="1" />藥<colour id="65535" />來給我，<delay8 />
我才舒服多了。<delay20 />
要不是這樣，<delay8 /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />恐怕會更難過吧<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也要<delay8 />保重身體喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實我今天一大早身體狀況就很糟……<delay frames="30" />
不過<delay20 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />多虧<tag a="115" b="0" arg="0xcd00" />帶了<colour id="1" />藥<colour id="65535" />給我，<delay8 />
現在已經好多了！<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我原本應該是<delay8 />不太會生病的體質，<delay20 />
但看來還是大意不得呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你睡覺的時候，<delay8 />可別露出肚子啊！<delay20 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 /><size value="75" />我就是這樣感冒的。<size value="100" /></message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然說起來很不好意思，<delay20 />
但我前陣子<delay8 />其實得了感冒……<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />多虧有<tag a="115" b="0" arg="0xcd00" />給我<colour id="1" />藥<colour id="65535" />，<delay8 />
所以我很快就好了，<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要不是這樣，<delay8 />恐怕就難過了<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也要<delay8 />保重身體喔！<tag a="110" b="6" /></message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對了，<delay8 />其實我前陣子發燒啦。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />多虧<tag a="115" b="0" arg="0xcd00" />帶了<colour id="1" />藥<colour id="65535" />給我，<delay8 />
所以我很快就好了。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我原本是<delay8 />不太會生病的體質，<delay20 />
但看來還是大意不得呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你睡覺的時候，<delay8 />可別露出肚子啊！<delay20 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 /><size value="75" />我就是這樣感冒的。<size value="100" /></message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為我<delay8 />家裡沒有準備<colour id="1" />藥<colour id="65535" />，<delay20 />
所以你帶來給我，<delay8 />真的是幫了大忙！<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實我一直昏昏沉沉的，<delay8 />
狀況真的很糟<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你真是我的<delay8 />救命恩人啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀～其實我家裡<delay20 />
沒有<delay8 />常備的<colour id="1" />藥<colour id="65535" />呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />原本還打算靠氣勢來跟病魔對抗，<delay20 />
但老實說，<delay8 />我也稍微有點不安呢。<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿嘿<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />真的很謝謝你！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有句俗話說<delay20 />「病由心生」，<delay20 />
所以我還以為病症<delay8 />只要靠幹勁就能趕跑了。<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看來還是<delay20 />盡早吃<colour id="1" />藥<colour id="65535" />盡早痊癒<delay8 />
才是最好的吧，<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>